0Mr%20Trudeau's%20clarification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20pretty%20big%20win%20for%20the%20Indian%20narrative...%20We%20had%20gone%20pretty%20hard.%20We%20had%20kicked%20out%20a%20diplomat%20and%20named%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bordman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heart%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20row%20remains%20unresolved%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Bordman%2C%20centring%20around%20perspectives%20on%20Nijjar's%20identity%20-%20whether%20he%20was%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%20as%20India%20claims%2C%20or%20a%20community%20activist%2C%20as%20many%20in%20Canada%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20geopolitical%20technicality%20aspect%2C%20India%20wins%20here%20because%20you%20never%20said%20you%20had%20evidence.%20But%20what%20does%20it%20change%20from%20the%20grand%20structures%20of%20things%3F%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20diplomatic%20spat%20is%20really%20about%20the%20unanswered%20question%2C%20was%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20or%20a%20community%20activist%3F%20And%20that%20general%20disagreement%20has%20not%20moved%2C%26quot%3B%20Bordman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bordman%20also%20criticised%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20claim%20that%20Canada%20supports%20India's%20territorial%20integrity.%20%26quot%3BTrudeau%20says%20things%20and%20then%20does%20things%20that%20don't%20align%20with%20what%20he%20says...%20He%20might%20claim%20to%20be%20against%20Khalistani%20separatism%2C%20but%20his%20actions%20tell%20a%20different%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bordman%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729140660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F33o00gkg_justin-trudeau-afp-_625x300_17_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-diplomatic-row-justin-trudeau-admits-canada-has-only-intel-no-evidence-in-nijjar-killing-6807798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20startling%20admission%20during%20a%20p