nessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis%2CSydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-reorganized-major-businesses-eliminated-roles-whatsapp-instagram-reality-labs-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202025%3A%20Big%20Stars%20Don't%20Want%20To%20Be%20Retained%20Due%20to%20This%20BCCI%20Rule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20diverse%20set%20of%20rules%20for%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20auction%20have%20reportedly%20created%20a%20big%20movement%20ahead%20of%20the%20retentions%20announcement%20on%20October%2031.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20option%20has%20allowed%20players%20to%20want%20to%20test%20their%20market%20value%20and%20choose%20to%20not%20be%20retained%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F132052%2Fhemang-badani-to-be-delhi-capitals-head-coach-for-next-two-seasons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20states%20that%20agents%20of%20several%20star%20players%2C%20particularly%20overseas%2C%20have%20been%20conducting%20discussions%20with%20other%20franchises%2C%20seeking%20to%20eke%20out%20the%20maximum%20market%20value%20for%20their%20clients.%20In%20such%20a%20case%2C%20they%20may%20not%20want%20to%20be%20retained%20and%20go%20against%20their%20original%20franchise's%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%202025%20retention%20rules%20allows%20franchises%20to%20have%20up%20to%20several%20RTM%20cards%2C%20which%20allows%20players%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20auction%20pool%20and%20be%20repurchased%20for%20a%20new%20fee%20instead%20of%20a%20designated%20retention%20slab.%20The%20new%20RTM%20rule%20even%20allows%20the%20final%20bid-winner%20to%20post%20a%20last%20extensive%20bid%20for%20the%20player%2C%20increasing%20their%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20Cricbuzz%20states%20that%20this%20new%20RTM%20rule%20has%20allowed%20player%20agents%20to%20open%20negotiations%20with%20both%20the%20original%20franchise%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20franchises%2C%20for%20better%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20effect%20of%20the%20new%20RTM%20rule%20may%20already%20be%20seen%2C%20with%20reports%20suggesting%20that%20IPL%202024%20runners-up%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20could%20be%20set%20to%20shell%20out%20Rs%2023%20crore%20to%20retain%20star%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Heinrich%20Klaasen%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F60210-heinrich-klaasen-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHeinrich%20Klaasen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Rs%2023%20cr%20is%20Rs%205%20cr%20more%20than%20the%20highest%20retention%20slab%20of%20Rs%2018%20cr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20Cricbuzz%20also%20states%20that%20the%20venue%20for%20the%20IPL%20auction%20could%20very%20likely%20be%20outside%20India.%20The%20frontrunners%20for%20this%20appear%20to%20be%20Saudi%20Arabian%20city%20or%20Singapore%2C%20while%20Austria's%20capital%20Vienna%20also%20stands%20an%20outside%20chance%20to%20be%20the%20auction%20host%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20maximum%20of%20six%20players%20can%20be%20retained%20by%20a%20franchise%2C%20either%20through%20direct%20retention%20or%20the%20RTM%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729130100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7rk27448_ipl-trophy-bcci_625x300_21_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-2025-report-makes-explosive-claim-about-big-stars-not-wanting-to-be-retained-due-to-this-bcci-rule-6805895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20RTM%20rule%20even%20allows%20the%20final%20bid-winner%20to%20post%20a%20last%20extensive%20bid%20for%20the%20player%2C%20increasing%20their%20price.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-2025-report-makes-explos