0Islands%20demanded%20tourism%20limits%20be%20enacted.%20In%20July%2C%20thousands%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-of-protesters-rallying-against-overtourism-in-barcelona-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarcelona%20to%20protest%20overtourism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20many%20blamed%20for%20the%20high%20costs%20of%20living%20in%20the%20city.%20Demonstrators%20shot%20tourists%20with%20water%20guns%20and%20shouted%20at%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20message%20alone%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20enough%20to%20significantly%20curb%20tourism%20numbers%2C%20according%20to%20Amir%20Eylon%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20Longwoods%20International%2C%20a%20market%20research%20consultancy%20that%20specializes%20in%20the%20travel%20tourism%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20where%20to%20go%2C%20where%20not%20to%20go%2C%20it's%20really%20the%20perception%20of%20safety%20that%20will%20drive%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Eylon%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20how%20tourists%20decide%20where%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Spain%20protests%20made%20headlines%2C%20tourists%20were%20not%20physically%20harmed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20created%20a%20negative%20safety%20perception%2C%20which%20he%20said%20historically%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20number%20of%20tourists%20choosing%20to%20visit%20a%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20a%20destination%20that%20many%20tourists%20plan%20and%20save%20for%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20tourists%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20deterred%20by%20these%20demonstrations%2C%20even%20if%20they%20do%20hear%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%2C%20however%2C%20could%20impact%20government%20policy%20in%20a%20way%20that%20may%20help%20curb%20or%20better%20manage%20tourism%20in%20the%20future%2C%20Eylon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf