%20height%3D%5C%223610%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENeal%20ended%20up%20becoming%20Nichole%20Wischoff's%20first%20full-time%20hire%2C%20beating%20over%20500%20applicants%20for%20the%20job.%3Cp%3ENeal%20Mintz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20interviewed%20Neal%20over%20three%20weeks.%20We%20had%20three%20calls%20before%20meeting%20in%20person.%20In%20addition%20to%20walking%20him%20through%20the%20job%2C%20I%20also%20brought%20him%20along%20to%20a%20founder%20pitch%20and%20got%20him%20to%20share%20his%20assessment%20with%20me%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20impressed%20me%20about%20Neal%20was%20how%20well-prepared%20he%20was.%20During%20our%20calls%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20Neal%20already%20knew%20a%20lot%20about%20my%20portfolio%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20the%20companies%20I've%20invested%20in%20or%20the%20areas%20I%20was%20excited%20about.%20He%20had%20detailed%20questions%20about%20specific%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20mentioned%20that%20I%20would%20have%20to%20set%20up%20a%20payroll%20system%20since%20I'd%20been%20operating%20the%20fund%20solo.%20Neal%20offered%20to%20help%20do%20it%20for%20free%2C%20showing%20just%20how%20much%20of%20a%20hustler%20he%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20say%20that%20Neal%20pretty%20much%20hired%20himself%20because%20he%20was%20really%20aggressive%2C%20in%20a%20good%20way%2C%20about%20landing%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcf0033e-b949-497d-b045-3deb20647c16%5C%22%3EI'm%20looking%20for%20people%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20run%20through%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20venture%20capital%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20be%20determined.%20Don't%20quit%2C%20and%20don't%20take%20no%20for%20an%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20be%20applying%20for%20a%20job%20or%20sourcing%20for%20a%20deal%2C%20you%20have%20to%20come%20in%20over-prepared%20for%20your%20meetings%20if%20you%20even%20want%20to%20stand%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%