%20wedding.%3Cp%3ELydia%20Koh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELydia%20Koh%20is%20a%20fine%20art%20wedding%20photographer%20and%20founder%20of%20a%20Singapore-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flydiakphotography.com%2F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephotography%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKoh%20said%20a%20timekeeper%20can%20help%20couples%20with%20a%20less%20stressful%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lesson%20from%20her%20own%20wedding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20also%20said%20couples%20often%20stress%20over%20preparations%20and%20overlook%20quality%20time%20with%20their%20guests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Lydia%20Koh%2C%20a%20wedding%20photographer.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20wedding%20photography%20in%202013%20when%20I%20attended%20a%20gorgeous%20wedding%20on%20a%20ranch%20in%20Southern%20California%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-mistakes-you-can-make-when-planning-an-outdoor-wedding-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esunset%20reception%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20standard%20Chinese%20weddings%20I%20was%20used%20to%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20inspired%20me%20to%20photograph%20more%20nontraditional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthy-couples-spend-money-wedding-planner-tradition-venue-entertainment-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutdoor%20weddings.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20I%20started%20my%20own%20photography%20business%2C%20managing%20everything%20from%20shooting%20and%20editing%20to%20marketing%20and%20occasional%20help%20from%20a%20colleague%20or%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I've%20learned%20from%20photographing%20weddings%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20biggest%20lesson%20came%20from%20my%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22424b614d-1938-4517-b6a4-501a24a33eb8%5C%22%3ECall%20a%20friend%20to%20keep%20the%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20pieces%20of%20advice%20I%20give%20my%20clients%20is%20to%20ensure%20they%20build%20in%20plenty%20of%20buffer%20time%20for%20their%20wedding%20shoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20not%20to%20cram%20too%20much%20into%20the%20timeline%20because%20things%20often%20go%20wrong%2C%20and%20one%20delay%20can%20easily%20affect%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day.%20Having%20that%20buffer%20is%20essential%20to%20prevent%20everything%20from%20running%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20cost-effective%20way%20to%20manage%20this%20is%20by%20appointing%20a%20timekeeper.%20Having%20someone%20responsible%20for%20keeping%20track%20of%20time%20helps%20ensure%20things%20stay%20on%20schedule%20without%20anyone%20getting%20flustered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20will%20want%20photos%20with%20the%20couple%20on%20the%20wedding%20day%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20to%20manage%20everything%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-guests-should-always-do-at-weddings-according-to-planner-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguests%3C%2Fa%3E%20ask%20for%20photos%20or%20try%20to%20pull%20the%20couple%20away%2C%20it's%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%20The%20timekeeper%20can%20step%20in%20and%20politely%20keep%20things%20on%20track%20to%20help%20the%20couple%20focus%20on%20enjoying%20their%20special%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20this%20lesson%20the%20hard%20way%20at%20my%20own%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20think%20we'd%20need%20a%20timekeeper%2C%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20my%20husband%20shouldered%20all%20the%20stress%20when%20things%20didn't%20go%20as%20planned.%20Miscommunication%20and%20poor%20time%20management%20left%20him%20stressed%20and%20flustered%2C%20unable%20to%20enjoy%20the%20day%20as%20he%20was%20constantly%20putting%20out%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20eventually%20fell%20behind%20schedule%20because%20guests%20continually%20came%20up%20to%20take%20photos%20with%20us.%20Not%20wanting%20to%20turn%20anyone%20down%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20running%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lost%20track%20of%20time%20and%20missed%20key%20moments%20without%20a%20timekeeper%20to%20manage%20the%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20someone%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20our%20time%20and%20manage%20guests'%20expectations%20is%20a%20good%20way%20for%20couples%20to%20be%20present%20and%20enjoy%20their%20wedding%20without%20worrying%20about%20logistics.%20After%20all%2C%20a%20wedding%20is%20about%20making%20memories%2C%20not%20managing%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf2ed1c5-cd5a-4385-979f-40150235ecbf%5C%22%3EHave%20enough%20time%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20too%20much%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-planning-mistakes-couples-make-according-to-photographer-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschedule%20enough%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20mingle%20with%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20as%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20meaningful%20parts%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20genuine%20moments%20happen%20when%20couples%20are%20relaxed%2C%20happy%2C%20and%20chatting%20with%20their%20guests.%20I%20always%20remind%20couples%20not%20to%20treat%20their%20wedding%20like%20a%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20they%20schedule%20too%20much%20time%20for%20multiple%20gown%20changes%2C%20missing%20out%20on%20spending%20time%20with%20their%20guests.%20They're%20stuck%20in%20the%20hotel%20room%20or%20changing%20area%20and%20don't%20experience%20the%20day%20fully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20crucial%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20wedding%20is%20about%20more%20than%20just%20looking%20good%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20being%20present%20with%20the%20people%20you%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20not%20to%20have%20a%20tight%20schedule%20and%20to%20leave%20buffer%20time%20for%20unexpected%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20wedding%2C%20technical%20issues%20caused%20our%20live%20musicians%20to%20start%20late%2C%20pushing%20back%20the%20entire%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20our%20venue%20had%20two%20floors%2C%20my%20husband%20constantly%20ran%20up%20and%20down%20stairs%20trying%20to%20fix%20things.%20The%20whole%20situation%20was%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20it%20kept%20him%20from%20fully%20enjoying%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20I%20always%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20building%20enough%20buffer%20time%20into%20the%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gives%20you%20room%20to%20handle%20unexpected%20delays%20without%20throwing%20off%20the%20entire%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20always%20tell%20my%20clients%20is%20not%20to%20start%20the%20day%20too%20early.%20There%20is%20a%20sweet%20spot%20between%20insufficient%20buffer%20time%20and%20too%20much%20of%20it.%20Couples%20that%20plan%20the%20day%20too%20early%20can%20quickly%20experience%20exhaustion%20by%20the%20time%20the%20reception%20arrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20on%20adrenaline%20only%20lasts%20so%20long%2C%20and%20tiredness%20can%20impact%20how%20much%20they%20enjoy%20the%20celebration.%20It's%20better%20to%20pace%20things%20and%20allow%20time%20to%20relax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-photographer-shares-2-secrets-avoid-stress-weddings-lydia-koh-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729123201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e1306a70318649281c50f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-photographer-shares-2-secrets-avoid-stress-weddings-lydia-koh-2024-10%22%2C%2