0Harris%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20rare%20interview%20with%20the%20Republican-leaning%20news%20channel%20during%20which%20she%20sparred%20with%20its%20popular%20host.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20point%20is%20that%20we%20have%20a%20broken%20immigration%20system%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20repaired%2C'%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Harris%20told%20Fox%20News%20anchor%20Bret%20Baier%20in%20a%20rare%20sit-down%20with%20the%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20your%20Homeland%20Security%20Secretary%20said%20that%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20apprehensions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Baier%20interjected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI'm%20not%20finished.%20We%20have%20an%20immigration%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Harris%20tried%20to%20continue%20with%20her%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20a%20rough%20estimate%20that%206%20million%20people%20have%20been%20released%20into%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Fox%20News%20anchor%20interrupted%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20let%20me%20just%20finish.%20I'll%20get%20to%20the%20question.%20I%20promise%20you.%20I%20was%20beginning%20to%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20vice%20president%20pleaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20came%20into%20office%2C%20your%20administration%20immediately%20reversed%20a%20number%20of%20Trump%20border%20policies.%20Most%20significantly%2C%20the%20policy%20that%20required%20illegal%20immigrants%20to%20be%20detained%20through%20deportation%2C%20either%20in%20the%20U.S.%20or%20in%20Mexico.%20And%20you%20switched%20that%20policy.%20They%20were...%20released%20from%20custody%20awaiting%20trial.%20So%20instead%2C%20included%20in%20those%20were%20a%20large%20number%20of%20single%20men%2C%20adult%20men%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20commit%20heinous%20crimes.%20So%20looking%20back%2C%20do%20you%20regret%20the%20decision%20to%20terminate%20Remain%20in%20Mexico%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20your%20administration%3F%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Baier%20asked%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%