.%20That's%20supposed%20to%20create%20what%20the%20company%20calls%20%26quot%3Bhigh-quality%20referrals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20churn%20by%20getting%20readers%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20the%20site%20since%20the%20biggest%20predictor%20of%20renewals%20is%20the%20number%20of%20articles%20a%20subscriber%20reads.%20Defector%20says%20%26quot%3Bonboarding%26quot%3B%20emails%20to%20new%20subscribers%2C%20pointing%20out%20articles%20and%20coverage%20they%20may%20not%20know%20about%2C%20has%20helped%20reduce%20churn%20by%20up%20to%2010%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20single%20thing%20is%20going%20to%20solve%20any%20of%20Defector's%20issues%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20trying%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%20Next%20up%3A%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefector%20has%20always%20been%20just%20about%20ad-free%2C%20with%20an%20occasional%20ad%20or%20sponsorship%20here%20and%20there.%20In%20their%20words%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20generally%20two%20ways%20to%20make%20money%20publishing%20words%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20we've%20largely%20ignored%20one%20of%20them%20so%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20the%20site%20thinks%20it's%20ready%20to%20try%20advertising%20for%20real%20and%20will%20start%20showing%20a%20regular%20diet%20of%20ads%20to%20non-subscribers%20later%20this%20year.%20It%20will%20hopefully%20be%20a%20twofer%20for%20the%20company%3A%20more%20revenue%2C%20derived%20primarily%20from%20readers%20who%20aren't%20likely%20to%20ever%20become%20subscribers%2C%20plus%20a%20gentle%20nudge%20that%20might%20prompt%20some%20non-subscribers%20to%20pay%20up%20to%20have%20a%20(mostly)%20ad-free%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%3A%20I%20don't%20often%20recommend%20annual%20financial%20reports%20as%20pleasure%20reading.%20But%20if%20you%20work%20in%20media%2C%20or%20are%20slightly%20curious%20about%20how%20the%20stuff%20on%20your%20screen%20gets%20to%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20hre