2%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Haryana%20Swearing-In%20Today%2C%20NDA's%20Mega%20Show%20Of%20Strength%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Opposition%20after%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20of%20all%20chief%20ministers%20and%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20from%20the%20coalition%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20immediately%20after%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20takes%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20for%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%2C%20which%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20will%20be%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20attended%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20among%20others.%20While%20India's%20development%20and%20celebrating%20the%20Constitution%20are%20also%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20a%20notable%20item%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20attempt%20to%20murder%20democracy%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Emergency%20-%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20being%20aimed%20squarely%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20alone%20has%2013%20chief%20ministers%20and%2016%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20and%20the%20others%20in%20attendance%20at%20the%20show%20of%20strength%20and%20unity%20will%20be%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Nagaland%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20who%20are%20from%20other%20NDA%20parties.%20A%20statement%20from%20the%20BJP%20said%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20will%20also%20%26quot%3Blead%20discussions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeliberations%20in%20this%20meeting%20will%20cover%20a%20structured%20agenda%20covering%20national%20development%20issues.%20It%20will%20also%20discuss%20subjects%20like%20the%20observance%20of%20Samvidhan%20Ka%20Amrut%20Mahotsav%20and%20the%20year%20of%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20attempt%20to%20murder%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%20Signalling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini's%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20and%20the%20meeting%20will%20both%20be%20held%20on%20Valmiki%20Jayanti%2C%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Maharishi%20Valmiki%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20Ramayan.%20The%20date%2C%20BJP%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20been%20carefully%20chosen%20to%20send%20a%20signal%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20whose%20vote%20was%20seen%20as%20having%20tilted%20towards%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2010%20years%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20240%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20with%20its%20emphasis%20on%20the%20Constitution%20and%20narrative%20that%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20the%20NDA%20to%20have%20400%20MPs%20so%20it%20could%20make%20amendments%20and%20%26quot%3Bend%20reservations%26quot%3B%2C%20bettered%20its%20tally%20to%2099%20while%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20as%20a%20whole%20won%20234.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition's%20pitch%20seemed%20to%20have%20worked%20in%20Haryana%20as%20well%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20was%20reduced%20to%20five%20out%20of%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20after%20its%202019%20clean%20sweep%2C%20but%20things%20had%20changed%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20Defying%20exit%20poll%20predictions%20and%20battling%20perceived%20anti-incumbency%20and%20anger%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20not%20only%20pull%20off%20a%20third%20straight%20win%20but%20also%20register%20its%20best-ever%20performance%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20said%20the%20Haryana%20elections%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20vote%20had%20returned%20to%20the%20party%20and%20the%20date%20of%20the%20swearing-in%20honours%20that.%20Dalit%20voters%20will%20also%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20uphill%20battle%20for%20the%20ruling%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena-NCP%20coalition%20but%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20made%20a%20little%20easier%20after%20the%20Haryana%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729103580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fnrvc3sg8_modi-naidu-nitish_625x300_05_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-chief-ministers-meeting-nda-chief-ministers-deputy-chief-ministers-after-haryana-swearing-in-tomorrow-ndas-mega-show-of-strength-6805709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Opposition%20after%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20of%20all%20chief%20ministers%20and%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20Chandigarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-chief-ministers-meeting-nda-chief-ministers-deputy-chief-ministers-after-haryana-swearing-in-tomorrow-ndas-mega-show-of-strength-6805709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nijjar%20killing%3A%20Trudeau%20admits%20he%20had%20no%20proof%20on%20Indian%20govt's%20involvement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729103283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fnijjar-killing-trudeau-admits-he-had-no-proof-on-indian-govt-s-involvement-124