%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-takes-oath-as-chief-minister-of-jammu-and-kashmir-6800528%5C%22%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompleted%20his%20education%20at%20the%20Burn%20Hall%20School%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20Lawrence%20School%20in%20Sanawar.%20He%20graduated%20with%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Commerce%20degree%20from%20Sydenham%20College%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Economics%20in%20Mumbai.%20Before%20his%20foray%20into%20politics%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20ITC%20Limited%20and%20The%20Oberoi%20Group.%20He%20enrolled%20in%20an%20MBA%20program%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Strathclyde%20but%20dropped%20out%20after%20his%20win%20in%20the%201998%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20with%20a%20rich%20legacy%20in%C2%A0politics.%20In%201998%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20his%20debut%2C%20Mr%20Abdulllah%2C%20all%20of%2028%2C%20became%20the%20youngest%20member%20of%20parliament%20at%20the%20time.%20His%20political%20career%20flourished%20as%20he%20was%20re-elected%20to%20the%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201999%20and%20appointed%20as%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20on%20October%2013%2C%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202001%2C%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20in%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20NDA%20government.%20However%2C%20he%20resigned%20in%20December%202002%20to%20focus%20on%20party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20a%20setback%20in%20the%202002%20state%20assembly%20elections%20where%20he%20lost%20his%20seat%20in%20Ganderbal.%20In%20March%202006%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20the%20then%20central%20government%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20met%20with%20Pakistan%20President%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20to%20discuss%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20issue.%C2%A0He%20became%20only%20the%20second%20member%20of%20his%20family%20to%20visit%20Pakistan.%20His%20grandfather%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%20also%20visited%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-assembly-election-result-omar-abdullah-ndtv-interview-pm-an-honourable-man-hope-he-omar-abdullahs-key-ask-after-j-k-win-6745271%5C%22%3EOmar%20Abdullah's%20Key%20Ask%20After%20J%26amp%3BK%20Win%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChief%20Minister%20Of%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%205%2C%202009%2C%20Omar%C2%A0Abdullah%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%2011th%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20leading%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20the%20Congress%20party.%20He%20succeeded%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20and%20became%20the%20youngest%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%20at%20age%2038.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost%20Chief%20Ministerial%20Career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20the%202014%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20continued%20to%20play%20an%20active%20role%20in%20politics.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20government's%20policies%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20was%20the%20last%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Legislative%20Assembly%20before%20the%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-polls-omar-abdullahs-fight-from-ganderbal-is-no-cakewalk-6501934%5C%22%3EOmar%20Abdullah's%20Fight%20From%20Ganderbal%20Is%20No%20Cakewalk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20And%20Controversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20faced%20significant%20challenges%20during%20his%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmarnath%20land%20row%20(2008)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%202008%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%C2%A0threatened%20to%20resign%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20due%20to%20the%20excessive%20use%20of%20force%20by%20security%20forces%20against%20protesters%20in%20Kashmir.%20His%20anger%20stemmed%20from%20the%20government's%20handling%20of%20the%20Amarnath%20land%20transfer%20issue%20and%20the%20subsequent%20economic%20blockade%20imposed%20by%20protestors%20in%20Jammu.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20if%20his%20concerns%20were%20not%20addressed%20by%20the%20government%2C%20he%20would%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20resign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShopian%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20(2009)%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOmar%20Abdullah%20faced%20backlash%20following%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20two%20women%20in%20Shopian.%20Initially%2C%20he%20supported%20the%20police's%20claim%20that%20the%20deaths%20were%20accidental%20drownings%2C%20causing%20public%20outrage.%20Although%20the%20police%20later%20retracted%20their%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20maintained%20his%20position%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20while%20downplaying%20allegations%20of%20foul%20play.%20The%20victims'%20families%20accused%20security%20forces%20of%20kidnapping%2C%20raping%20and%20killing%20the%20women.%20The%20opposition%2C%20particularly%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20criticised%20Omar%20Abdullah%20for%20prematurely%20concluding%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKashmir%20unrest%20(2010)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Omar%20Abdullah%20government%20faced%20criticism%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20unrest%2C%20which%20killed%20over%20100%20protesters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHanging%20of%20Afzal%20Guru%20(2013)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20February%209%2C%202013%2C%20Mohammad%20Afzal%20Guru%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20separatist%2C%20was%20hanged%20to%20death%20at%20Tihar%20Jail%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%202001%20Indian%20Parliament%20attack.%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20faced%20the%20blowback%2C%20which%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20severe%20protests%20and%20debates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20Safety%20Act%20(2020)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20detained%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA)%20on%20February%207%2C%202020%2C%20amid%20the%20lockdown%20imposed%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20He%20was%20released%20in%20March%20of%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729097820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvoga1hr_omar-abdullah_625x300_16_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-back-as-jammu-and-kashmir-chief-minister-after-10-years-6803953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Omar%20Abdullah%20entered%20politics%20in%201998%20when%20he%20was%20elected%20to%20the%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20age%20of%2028%2C%20the%20youngest%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-back-as-jammu-and-kashmir-chief-minister-after-10-years-6803953%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMost%20Talented%20Cricketer%26quot%3B%3A%20Kohli's%20Big%20Admission.%20Not%20From%20India%2C%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20South%20African%20legend%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22AB%20de%20Villiers%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F699-ab-de-villiers-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAB%20de%20Villiers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20known%20as%20'Mr%20360'%2C%20England%20batting%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Alastair%20Cook%5C%2