030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hezbollah%20war%20has%20left%20at%20least%201%2C373%20people%20dead%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20Lebanese%20health%20ministry%20figures%2C%20though%20the%20real%20toll%20is%20likely%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran-backed%20Hezbollah%20started%20low-intensity%20strikes%20on%20Israel%20in%20October%20last%20year%20in%20support%20of%20its%20ally%20Hamas%2C%20following%20its%20October%207%20attack%20that%20triggered%20the%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Hamas%20weakened%20but%20not%20defeated%2C%20Israel%20widened%20the%20focus%20of%20its%20military%20operations%20to%20include%20Lebanon%2C%20vowing%20to%20fight%20until%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20forced%20by%20Hezbollah's%20fire%20to%20flee%20their%20homes%20are%20able%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael%20striking%20nuclear%20sites%20'unlikely'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20has%20also%20braced%20for%20Israel's%20promised%20retaliation%20against%20its%20arch-foe%20Iran%20for%20launching%20around%20200%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20on%20October%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20said%20the%20attack%20was%20itself%20retaliation%20for%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Beirut%20days%20before%20that%20killed%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20and%20Iranian%20general%20Abbas%20Nilforoushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20warned%20Israel%20against%20striking%20Iran's%20nuclear%20or%20oil%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20of%20Iran's%20atomic%20agency%2C%20Behrouz%20Kamalvandi%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20an%20Israeli%20attack%20on%20key%20Iranian%20nuclear%20sites%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unlikely%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Israel%20were%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20a%20stupid%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Iran%20could%20%26quot%3Bquickly%20compensate%26quot%3B%20for%20any%20potential%20damage%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETehran%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20retaliate%20if%20Israel%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%20on%20Israel%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Netanyahu%20told%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bopposed%20to%20a%20unilateral%20ceasefire%2C%20which%20does%20not%20change%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20Lebanon%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20then%20called%20Macron%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisgrace%26quot%3B%20after%20Israeli%20delegations%20were%20banned%20from%20exhibiting%20hardware%20at%20a%20defence%20show%20being%20held%20in%20France%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20--%20Israel's%20top%20arms%20supplier%20--%20has%20also%20criticised%20Israel's%20air%20strikes%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20clear%20that%20we%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20campaign%20the%20way%20we've%20seen%20it%20conducted%20over%20the%20past%20weeks%26quot%3B%20in%20Beirut%2C%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20faced%20criticism%20over%20injuries%20and%20damage%20sustained%20by%20UNIFIL%2C%20the%20UN%20peacekeeping%20force%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%2016%20European%20Union%20defence%20ministers%20called%20%26quot%3Bfor%20maximum%20political%20and%20diplomatic%20pressure%20on%20Israel%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20further%20incidents%20against%20peacekeepers%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Foreign%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20said%20his%20country%20%26quot%3Bplaces%20great%20importance%20on%20the%20activities%20of%20UNIFIL%20and%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20harming%20the%20organisation%20or%20its%20personnel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lebanese%20Red%20Cross%20said%20two%20paramedics%20were%20wounded%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20south%20Lebanon%20v