%20operations%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESemchan%20has%20a%20team%20of%20eight%20workers%20who%20operate%20the%20rescue%20shelter%20daily.%20This%20includes%20maintaining%20the%20resident%20dogs%2C%20maintaining%20the%20facility%2C%20rescuing%20injured%20and%20ill%20dogs%2C%20picking%20up%20dogs%20for%20sterilisation%2C%20and%20operating%20a%20feeding%20programme%20for%20up%20to%20700%20dogs%20in%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shelter%20contains%20about%20eight%20pens%2C%20plus%20a%20large%20central%20area%20where%20dogs%20can%20move%20around.%C2%A0%20There%20are%20approximately%20170%20dogs%20but%20this%20number%20changes%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nurzin%20Angmo%20(on%20the%20Left)%20and%20Binod%20(on%20the%20Right)%20applying%20ointment%20on%20a%20sick%20dog%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENurzin%20Angmo%20(on%20the%20Left)%20and%20Binod%20(on%20the%20Right)%20applying%20ointment%20on%20a%20sick%20dog%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigu