rent%20pens.%20For%20instance%2C%20older%20dogs%20and%20dogs%20receiving%20medication%20and%20treatments%20are%20grouped%20in%20the%20largest%20pen%20measuring%20100%20x%20100%20feet.%20Dogs%20which%20are%20younger%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20more%20active%2C%20are%20housed%20in%20a%20separate%20pen.%C2%A0Young%20pups%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20grouped%20in%20another%20pen.%20One%20pen%20is%20specifically%20dedicated%20to%20a%20Tibetan%20Mastiff.%20On%20the%20outside%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20aggressive%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20owner%20had%20to%20surrender%20him%20because%20he%20had%20bitten%20several%20people.%20We%20gave%20him%20his%20own%20pen%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20female%20dogs%2C%20and%20he%20gets%20along%20fine%20with%20them%20and%20the%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESemchan%E2%80%99s%20unique%20approach%20to%20stray%20dog%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20rescue%20service%20has%20become%20pretty%20well-known%20in%20Leh.%20Our%20phone%20number%20is%20available%20in%20the%20community%2C%20so%20people%20call%20the%20team.%20The%20caller%20is%20asked%20to%20send%20a%20picture%20or%20video%20of%20the%20dog%20needing%20rescue%20and%20to%20stay%20there%20with%20the%20dog%20while%20we%20come.%20Usually%2C%20two%20men%20take%20the%20van%2C%20which%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20cage%20for%20capturing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20uses%20careful%20and%20compassionate%20capture%20methods%2C%20almost%20always%20without%20nets%20or%20ropes.%20They%20usually%20cover%20the%20dog%20with%20a%20blanket%2C%20scoop%20it%20up%20into%20their%20arms%2C%20and%20quickly%20put%20it%20into%20the%20cage.%20Then%20we%20take%20the%20dog%20to%20the%20government%20veterinary%20hospital%20for%20examination%20and%2For%20treatment.%20Once%20the%20vets%20release%20the%20dog%20for%20aftercare%2C%20we%20bring%20it%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328239%2Fanimal-rescue-and-rehabilitation-centres-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Rescue%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ARC)%2C%20where%20we%20follow%20up%20with%20the%20prescribed%20medications%2C%20nutrition%2C%20rest%2C%20and%20safety%2C%20and%20follow-up%20visits%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Injured%20stray%20dogs%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20need%20their%20leg%20amputated%20and%20the%20rehab%20is%20for%20healing%20the%20wound.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20further%2C%20Nurzin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20rescues%20are%20injuries%20from%20road%20accidents.%20Many%20of%20these%20dogs%20have%20broken%20bones%20and%20need%20casts%20and%20rehab%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Some%2C%20however%2C%20need%20to%20get%20their%20leg%20amputated.%20Other%20cases%20include%20dogs%20suffering%20from%20different%20illnesses%2C%20etc.%20Occasionally%20there%20is%20an%20unusual%20rescue%2C%20where%20a%20dog%20is%20trapped%20in%20a%20hole.%20Our%20people%20are%20terrific%20at%20handling%20these%20situations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369884%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20approximately%20170%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter%20but%20this%20number%20changes%20all%20the%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20such%20rescue%20episode%2C%20Deena%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20time%2C%20some%20young%20women%20called%20us%20for%20help.%20A%20mother%20dog%20had%20delivered%20four%20pups%20in%20a%20small%20room%20in%20an%20abandoned%20building.%20She%20nursed%20them%20till%20they%20were%20about%20three%20months%20old%2C%20then%20the%20mother%20was%20out%20one%20day%20and%20someone%20plastered%20over%20the%20entrance%20and%20the%20pups%20were%20trapped%20inside%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20team%20arrived%2C%20we%20assessed%20the%20problem.%20Finally%2C%20one%20member%20was%20able%20to%20squeeze%20his%20body%20through%20a%20tiny%20window%20into%20the%20room%20and%20hand%20the%20pups%20out%2C%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20We%20took%20them%20to%20ARC%20and%20cared%20for%20them.%20They%20had%20never%20really%20seen%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20or%20been%20around%20people%20or%20other%20dogs.%20They%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20adjustment%2C%20and%20they%20gradually%20became%20normal%20little%20pups.%20Two%20of%20them%20died%20some%20months%20later%20for%20different%20reasons%2C%20and%20two%20of%20them%20are%20living%20just%20fine%20now%20at%20ARC%20more%20than%20a%20year%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENurturing%20trust%20between%20dogs%20and%20humans%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20stands%20out%20about%20this%20particular%20rescue%20shelter%20is%20how%20comfortable%20these%20dogs%20are%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20(human)%20strangers.%20On%20a%20personal%20visit%20to%20the%20shelter%20in%20September%202022%2C%20it%20was%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20easy%20and%20comfortable%20it%20was%20to%20enter%20the%20dog%20pens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENurzin%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20remarked%20on%20this%20aspect.%20We%20often%20take%20first-time%20visitors%20right%20inside%20the%20pens%20to%20meet%20the%20dogs.%20Also%2C%20quite%20a%20number%20of%20dogs%20are%20usually%20roaming%20freely%20in%20the%20central%20area%20and%20the%20area%20right%20in%20front%20of%20our%20little%20house.%20It%20is%20amazing%20to%20us%20that%20none%20of%20them%20are%20aggressive%20towards%20people%20and%20except%20for%20a%20few%20shy%20ones%2C%20they%20are%20friendly%20with%20strangers.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20that%20they%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caring%20for%20a%20stray%20dog.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENurzin%20Angmo%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20that%20they%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-huCGhyVKX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-huCGhyVKX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-huCGhyVKX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20semchan%20welfare%20society%20(%40semchanwelfaresociety)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20explains%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20safe%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%20We%20start%20by%20hiring%20members%20who%20we%20have%20an%20inkling%20will%20be%20good%20with%20animals%2C%20and%20bring%20some%20love%20and%20care%20to%20the%20work.%20Then%20we%20set%20examples%20and%20policies%20to%20encourage%20those%20attitudes%2C%20and%20our%20managers%20are%20constantly%20training%20in%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20such%20care.%20We%20give%20each%20dog%20a%20name%20and%20keep%20a%20paper%20record%20of%20each%20one%20with%20its%20picture%20on%20the%20page.%20The%20team%20members%20use%20the%20names%2C%20and%20converse%20with%20each%20other%20about%20the%20progress%20the%20dogs%20are%20making%2C%20the%20medications%20they%20are%20taking%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20all%20team%20members%20as%20many%20different%20duties%20as%20possible%3A%20feeding%2C%20administering%20medicines%2C%20cleaning%20cages%20and%20pens%2C%20keeping%20records%20of%20care%2C%20maintaining%20infrastructure%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20going%20out%20for%20rescues%2C%20etc.%20Everyone%20is%20encouraged%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20dogs%2C%20examine%20their%20bodies%20for%20any%20new%20problems%2C%20cuddle%20with%20them%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20So%2C%20a%20member%20who%20may%20not%20have%20experience%20with%20hands-on%20dog%20care%20will%20learn%20it%20by%20the%20good%20examples%20set%20by%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20of%20mass%20feeding%20stray%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20initiatives%20taken%20by%20Semchan%20is%20the%20feeding%20of%20dogs%20not%20just%20housed%20at%20the%20rescue%20shelter%20but%20across%20different%20feeding%20centres%20in%20Leh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feed%20about%20300%20dogs%20in%20the%20summer%20months%20and%20in%20the%20last%20winter%20season%2C%20we%20fed%20about%20650%20(one%20feeding%20session%20a%20day)%20across%2027%20feeding%20stations.%20We%20prepare%20the%20food%20in%20our%20kitchen%2C%20consisting%20of%20rice%20mixed%20with%20dry%20dog%20food%2C%20chicken%2C%20and%20a%20water%2Fmilk%20portion%20to%20soften%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20canine%20experts%20have%20expressed%20their%20concern%20about%20mass%20feeding%2C%20and%20how%20it%20exacerbates%20the%20growing%20conflict%20between%20dogs%20and%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20past%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319519%2Fwhy-india-struggles-to-deal-with-street-stray-dogs-animal-rights-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Abi%20Tamim%20Vanak%2C%20an%20animal%20ecologist%20and%20conservation%20biologist%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20%5Bnecessarily%5D%20provocation%2C%20but%20pack%20formation%20that%20leads%20to%20deadly%20%5Bstray%20dog%5D%20attacks%20on%20people.%20And%20why%20does%20pack%20formation%20happen%3F%20It%20happens%20whenever%20you%20have%20massive%20resources%20gathered%20in%20one%20place.%20Feeding%20one%20or%20two%20dogs%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20when%20you%20feed%20five%2C%20seven%2C%20or%20ten%20dogs%20at%20one%20location%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20pack%20formation%20occurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeena%2C%20however%2C%20disagrees%20with%20this%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescued%20stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-6-Doggies-1-1728640657-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERescued%20stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHungry%20dogs%20become%20aggressive%20dogs.%20In%20our%20experience%2C%20feeding%20helps%20in%20keeping%20the%20dog%20population%20calm%20and%20content%20and%20does%20not%20encourage%20attacks.%20If%20there%20had%20been%20any%20attacks%20on%20humans%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20we%20feed%2C%20the%20Government%20would%20have%20contacted%20us.%20We%20have%20not%20received%20any%20such%20notification.%20During%20winter%2C%20we%20feed%20between%201%20pm%20and%205%20pm%20so%20that%20the%20dogs%20are%20not%20hungry%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20amid%20rising%20dog%20bite%20cases%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Union%20Territory%20Government%20of%20Ladakh%20issued%20an%20order%20in%20July%202024%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20armed%20forces%20establishments%2C%20hotels%2C%20homestays%2C%20restaurants%2C%20guest%20houses%20in%20Leh%20district%20shall%20strictly%20refrain%20from%20throwing%20leftover%20foods%20on%20the%20roads%20and%20other%20places%20reachable%20by%20feral%20dogs.%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20given%20for%20this%20order%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccases%20of%20feral%20dog%20bites%20have%20gone%20up%20exponentially%2C%20thereby%20posing%20a%20risk%20to%20public%20safety%20and%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMass%20feeding%20is%20a%20delicate%20issue%20that%20requires%20greater%20scientific%20scrutiny%20and%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommitment%20to%20dog%20care%20and%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20paying%20for%20food%20and%20the%20fuel%20costs%20incurred%20during%20rescues%2C%20Semchen%20also%20incurs%20the%20cost%20of%20spaying%20and%20sterilising%20dogs%20via%20a%20private%20vet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20a%20Vet%20Tech%20comes%20every%20evening%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20to%20bandage%20the%20dogs.%20They%20also%20obtain%20vaccines%20to%20protect%20dogs%20from%20the%20Parvovirus%20%5Ba%20highly%20contagious%20disease%20that%20can%20affect%20dogs%5D%20that%20come%20in%20from%20Pune.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20no%20cases%20of%20Parvo%20since%20March-April%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20is%20a%20strong%20commitment%20to%20care%20and%20rehabilitation%20at%20Semchan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-12-1-1728641956-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369903%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20strong%20commitment%20to%20care%20and%20rehabilitation%20at%20Semchan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caring%20for%20injured%20stray%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-3-Rehab-1-1728640758-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads