figcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sales%20were%20very%20good%20this%20year%2C%20Lohith%20attributes%20it%20to%20a%20good%20yield.%20However%2C%20the%20yield%20might%20not%20be%20the%20same%20every%20year.%20Climate%20change%20leading%20to%20erratic%20rainfall%20has%20caused%20it%20to%20vary%20in%20certain%20years%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lohith%20is%20not%20working%20his%20farm%2C%20he%20runs%20a%20nursery%2C%20selling%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%20and%20durian%20plants.%20He%20also%20manages%20plants%20for%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307016%2Finspired-by-facebook-video-gardener-grows-brazilian-exotic-fruits-in-kerala-learnt-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20these%20exotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20the%20plants%2C%20maintain%20it%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20once%20it%20starts%20giving%20a%20good%20yield%2C%20the%20owners%20take%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20to%20becoming%20a%20millionaire%2C%20Lohith%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20testimony%20to%20the%20power%20of%20innovation%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Lohith%20Shetty%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728644313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-85-min-1728642767.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lohith%20Shetty%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Dakshina%20Kannada%20district%20in%20Karnataka%20started%20growing%20exotic%20fruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20dragonfruit%2C%20mangosteen%20on%20his%20family%20farm%2C%20earning%20handsome%20profits.%20Today%2C%20he%20runs%20a%20nursery%20too%20and%20teaches%20others%20how%20to%20