%20preventing%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20runs%20a%2024x7%20helpline%20and%20provides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%20one-stop%20centres.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20runs%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20and%20provides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%20one-stop%20centres.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Break%20the%20intergenerational%20cycle%20of%20crime%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20says%20that%20whatever%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20spouse%20should%20not%20resort%20to%20heinous%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20acceptable%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20home%20is%20a%20place%20where%20you%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20loved%20and%20cared%20for.%20Children%20in%20such%20families%20are%20also%20affected%20as%20they%20are%20silent%20witnesses%20to%20the%20crime.%20Growing%20up%2C%20they%20assume%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20normal%20life%20is%20about.%20When%20such%20kids%20date%20or%20are%20in%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20they%20express%20love%20and%20anger%20in%20ways%20they%20learn%20from%20their%20own%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20family%20must%20take%20responsibility%20%E2%80%94%20in%20how%20we%20communicate%20at%20home%2C%20how%20we%20raise%20our%20children%2C%20and%20how%20we%20ensure%20equality%20in%20the%20upbringing%20of%20both%20girls%20and%20boys.%20The%20way%20parents%20argue%20and%20shout%20in%20front%20of%20children%20matters.%20Otherwise%2C%20this%20behaviour%20risks%20becoming%20an%20intergenerational%20cycle%20of%20violence%2C%20where%20children%20grow%20up%20to%20become%20perpetrators%20themselves.%20We%20need%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Teach%20children%20about%20respectful%20relationships%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20education%20in%20combating%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20certain%20attitude%20that%20normalises%20violence.%20To%20change%20it%2C%20we%20must%20focus%20on%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchools%20can%20play%20a%20very%20big%20role%20in%20educating%20kids%20about%20respectful%20relationships%20through%20specially%20designed%20programmes.%20Schools%20can%20also%20help%20hold%20perpetrators%20accountable%20by%20organising%20programmes%20that%20make%20them%20understand%20the%20impact%20and%20the%20damage%20they%20inflict%20on%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Do%20not%20treat%20domestic%20abuse%20survivors%20as%20cheap%20labour%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20people%20reach%20out%20to%20Prasanna%20offering%20jobs%20such%20as%20taking%20care%20of%20senior%20citizens%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20working%20as%20domestic%20helpers%2C%20or%20stitching%20bags%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20not%20all%20survivors%20of%20violence%20can%20stitch%20bags%20for%20a%20living.%20If%20a%20survivor%20decides%20to%20leave%20the%20perpetrator%20and%20become%20financially%20independent%20to%20take%20care%20of%20herself%20and%20their%20children%2C%20we%20cannot%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20can%20be%20a%20source%20of%20cheap%20labour%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20believes%20that%20every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths%2C%20and%20opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20those%20strengths.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369242%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20believes%20that%20every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths%2C%20and%20opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20those%20strengths.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20this.%20Every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths.%20Opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20that%20strength.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20be%20educated%2C%20we%20should%20encourage%20them%20to%20finish%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Sensitise%20the%20local%20officials%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20sensitise%20police%20and%20other%20support%20systems.%20If%20cases%20of%20domestic%20violence%20or%20sexual%20violence%20are%20informed%20to%20them%2C%20they%20need%20to%20respond%20with%20utmost%20care%20and%20urgency.%20It%20is%20not%20like%20dealing%20with%20regular%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20opines%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Support%20your%20neighbours%20experiencing%20abuse%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20government%20officials%2C%20Prasanna%20believes%20it%20is%20our%20shared%20responsibility%20to%20not%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20when%20these%20incidents%20happen%2C%20neighbours%20feel%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20their%20place%20to%20intervene.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20duty%20to%20offer%20support.%20We%20need%20to%20organise%20programmes%20and%20discussions%20that%20actively%20involve%20community%20members%20in%20decision-making%20and%20foster%20a%20collective%20effort%20to%20tackle%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20assistance%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Prasanna%20through%20the%20Dhwani%20National%20Domestic%20Violence%20Hotline%20at%201800-102-7282%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%