erpetrators%20are%20writing%20to%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98Do%20what%20you%20like%2C%20I%20know%20the%20Police%20will%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%99%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20the%20police%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%20anything%3B%20it%20is%20just%20the%20volume%20of%20cases%20and%20the%20anonymity%20that%20online%20media%20allows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20platforms%20are%20also%20not%20very%20prompt%20in%20collaborating%20and%20sharing%20information.%20We%20have%20been%20informed%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20guidelines%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20or%20child%20is%20subjected%20to%20derogatory%20images%20being%20circulated%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20contact%20the%20grievance%20officer%20for%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20getting%20responses%20is%20often%20challenging.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20report%20on%20the%20app%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%20the%20response%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20violate%20their%20community%20guidelines%20or%20something%20similar.%20Even%20if%20an%20account%20is%20taken%20down%2C%20how%20long%20does%20it%20take%20for%20the%20perpetrator%20to%20create%20another%20one%3F%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202016-17%20I%20was%20part%20of%20a%20television%20show%20about%20tracking%20down%20these%20trolls%20who%20troll%20celebrities.%20Basically%2C%20the%20objective%20was%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20anonymity%20is%20a%20myth%20online.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20we%20would%20be%20successful.%20I%E2%80%99d%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%2080-20%3B%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20you%20can%2C%2020%25%20of%20the%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTechnology%20is%20improving.%20It%20is%20becoming%20much%20more%20difficult%20(to%20trace%20down%20perpetrators).%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20always%20possible%20to%20track%20them%20down%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20time-consuming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAddressing%20cyberbullying%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Pritha%20and%20Priya%20agree%20that%20the%20first%20step%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20combat%20this%20menace%20is%20to%20confide%20in%20someone.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20talk%20to%20someone%2C%20that%20is%20primary%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20for%20many%20people%2C%20reaching%20out%20and%20talking%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirali%20sees%20the%20blockade%20from%20societal%20stigma%20as%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20countering%20a%20menace%20that%20she%20believes%20is%20a%20pandemic.%20The%20NHRC%20data%20supports%20her%20claims.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20fallen%20victim%20to%20the%20malicious%20trolls%20that%20make%20the%20internet%20a%20dark%20place%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20steps%20you%20should%20take%2C%20starting%20with%20talking%20to%20someone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20never%20in%20the%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says%2C%20explaining%20that%20sharing%20an%20incident%20with%20a%20loved%20one%20can%20help%20alleviate%20guilt%20and%20lead%20to%20concrete%20steps%20the%20victim%20can%20take.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20foolproof%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20acknowledges%20but%20asserts%20that%20women%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20feel%20guilty%20or%20ashamed%20because%20of%20a%20pervert%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20like%20morphing%20their%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20you%3B%20it%20is%20not%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20adds.%20As%20time%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20internet%20will%20increasingly%20dictate%20our%20lives%20more%20than%20the%20streets%20do.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20harassment%20is%20harassment%2C%20and%20bullying%20is%20bullying%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20physical%20or%20virtual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%